        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="6.756418508" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on data from United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (comtrade.un.org). UN comtrade category: 3808 Insecticides, rodenticides, fungicides, herbicides, anti-sprouting products, plant growth regulators, disinfectants and the like, put up in forms or packings for retail sale or as preparations or articles. Average of years 2015-2019. Average of price of import into 5 main markets (EU, US, JP, CN and BR, based on OEC, https://oec.world/en/profile/hs/pesticides). Last accessed 2022-08-16.
The prices were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2022-02-15) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=sts_inpp_a&amp;lang=en, last accessed on 2022-05-04).</comment>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="a9358458-9724-4f03-b622-106eda248916" amount="0.0" isDefiningValue="true" unitId="577e242a-461f-44a7-922c-d8e1c3d2bf45">
