        <name xml:lang="en">Water, salt, sole</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">m3</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">There are intermediates containing bromine and iodine in this process and this input is used as an input in the bromine and iodine production.

The concentration of bromine in water, salt, sole is 0.23% = 0.0023kg/kg. Cross-referenced: 0.25% (Ullmann's encyclopedia), 0.4% (USGS). The concentration of iodine in water, salt, sole is 0.03% = 0.0003kg/kg. Cross-referenced: 0.015% - 0.12% (Ullmann's encyclopedia).
There are intermediates containing bromine and iodine in this process and this input is used as an input in the bromine and iodine production.

The concentration of bromine in water, salt, sole is 0.23% = 0.0023kg/kg. Cross-referenced: 0.25% (Ullmann's encyclopedia), 0.4% (USGS). The concentration of iodine in water, salt, sole is 0.03% = 0.0003kg/kg. Cross-referenced: 0.015% - 0.12% (Ullmann's encyclopedia).</comment>
        <uncertainty>
